>\n<p>Linux 客户端官方只做了 ubuntu 的兼容，而我用的是 manjaroKDE + Mac 。装的这个 <strong>yay -S parsec-bin</strong></p>\n<p>现在的问题是，Linux 可以连 Mac ，但是 Mac 不能连 manjaro ，因为 Linux 没有 host 这个模式（没有相关设置选项），<img alt=\"host\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24egy1h13pw9kzmjj21g90u0jus.jpg\"/>也就是说没办法当主机，只能当客户端连接别人，不能被连接，很喜欢这个软件，有办法解决吗？或者有没有类似的软件？</p>\n<p>mac 是 bugsur + amd 的显卡。manjaroKDE 是 gtx1070 显卡</p>\n", "last_modified": 1649505816, "replies": 49, "id": 845934}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b789/2fb3/937_large.png?m=1584298330", "name": "zhihu", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b789/2fb3/937_normal.png?m=1584298330", "title": "知乎", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/zhihu", "topics": 374, "footer": "", "header": "知乎创建于 2010 年，是一个用户产生内容的问答社区", "title_alternative": "Zhihu", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b789/2fb3/937_mini.png?m=1584298330", "stars": 99, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 937, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 279313, "username": "night98", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/night98", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2d2031c324fac84b13ba4dbb1fa2e655?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2d2031c324fac84b13ba4dbb1fa2e655?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2d2031c324fac84b13ba4dbb1fa2e655?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1514980262, "last_modified": 1647870672}, "last_reply_by": "kingjpa", "last_touched": 1649581086, "title": "知乎也有黑洞了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/845930", "created": 1649505049, "deleted": 0, "content": "热榜上某复旦小哥写程序的题\r\n\r\n看完之后实在忍不住吐槽了一下疫情的系统性问题，发布完之后特意加推了一下，过了半小时一看 1 阅读 0 点赞，打开回答一看是正常的，遂复制地址栏用无痕模式打开，显示此回答已被删除\r\n\r\n2022 年了，想说点真话挺难的", "content_rendered": "<p>热榜上某复旦小哥写程序的题</p>\n<p>看完之后实在忍不住吐槽了一下疫情的系统性问题，发布完之后特意加推了一下，过了半小时一看 1 阅读 0 点赞